OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773911088
OL,3,CMore than 60 firefighters at scene of
OL,4,Cthatch roof fire
OL,6,FMore than 60 firefighters are tackling
OL,7,Fa thatched roof fire in Hampshire.
OL,9,FCrews were called to Viables Lane in
OL,10,FBasingstoke at around 4pm on Tuesday
OL,11,FFebruary 17. They remain at the scene.
OL,13,FEngines from Basingstoke, Rushmoor,
OL,14,FAndover, Winchester, Hartley Witney
OL,15,Fand Alton are attending the incident.
OL,17,FHampshire Fire and Rescue Service have
OL,18,Fconfirmed that nobody was present at
OL,19,Fthe property when the fire was
OL,20,Freported.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
