OL,3,CMore than 60 firefighters at scene of
OL,4,Cthatch roof fire
OL,6,FThe cause of the fire is currently
OL,7,Funknown, the service added.
OL,9,FLocals are being asked to avoid the
OL,10,Farea where possible as a large number
OL,11,Fof emergency service vehicles are
OL,12,Fattending the scene.
OL,14,FA statement from Hampshire Fire and
OL,15,FRescue Service said: "We are currently
OL,16,Ftackling a thatched roof fire on
OL,17,FViables Lane in Basingstoke.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
