PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773911088
OL,3,CMore than 60 firefighters at scene of
OL,4,Cthatch roof fire
OL,6,F"Over 60 firefighters are on scene
OL,7,Ftackling the blaze, using Compressed
OL,8,FAir Foam (CAFS) and jets to extinguish
OL,9,Fthe flames and prevent further fire
OL,10,Fspread."
OL,12,FVictoria Strowger, Assistant Director
OL,13,FService Delivery at Hampshire Fire and
OL,14,FRescue Service, told ITV Meridian how
OL,15,Ffirefighters are currently tackling
OL,16,Fthe blaze.
OL,18,F'Our main consideration was that
OL,19,Fsalvage to get all of the belongings
OL,20,Fthat we could out of the property for
OL,21,Fthe property owners'
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
