CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773911088
OL,3,CMore than 60 firefighters at scene of
OL,4,Cthatch roof fire
OL,6,FShe said: "So, we've got firefighters
OL,7,Fat the front of the property and
OL,8,Ffirefighters at the back of the
OL,9,Fproperty.
OL,11,F"So, our main consideration was that
OL,12,Fsalvage to get all of the belongings
OL,13,Fthat we could out of the property for
OL,14,Fthe property owners.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
